data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a prime location with breathtaking mountain views, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom gem offers everything you Step into your dream home! This stunning 3 bed, 2.5 bath gem is in a prime location with jaw-dropping mountain views. As you step inside, you'll be instantly captivated by the open floor plan, featuring a spacious great room and a welcoming foyer that sets the stage for an extraordinary living experience.    The heart of this home lies in the incredible kitchen, complete with a convenient island and top-of-the-line appliances. Whip up delicious meals while entertaining your loved ones and create memories that will last a lifetime. And let's not forget about the walk-in closets! Prepare to be amazed by the abundant storage space that will keep your belongings perfectly organized.    Imagine retreating to your own private oasis in the primary suite, which boasts a luxurious spa shower to wash away the day's stresses. Chores have never been easier or more efficient with a laundry area conveniently located upstairs. You can also enjoy additional modern comforts like a water heater and air conditioner.    Outside the walls, you'll discover a charming front porch and patio area, perfect for basking in the sun or savoring a cup of coffee while admiring the majestic mountains in the distance. And if location is a priority, you'll be delighted to know that this home offers easy access to I-25, Ft. Carson, and Peterson SFB. Plus, it's within walking distance of schools, making it the ideal choice for busy families. Get ready to live the life you've always dreamed of - this home has it all!
